      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUMMA EASY (3) is a first starter from the Andrea Chapple yard by Aston Dee Bee out of Nice And Easy. Lot to like about her profile and expected to run well. BOMB PETER (7) turned in a solid run last start over 515m at Sandown finishing 4th and beaten only 1.5 lengths (30.90). Yet to win here but has run some good races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Should be in this for a long way. JUMBUK FUNI (2) was a fast winner last time with a dominant 8 lengths win (19.61) at this track. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Leading chance again. LOST YOURS TOO (1) was out of the frame here on debut but can atone with the right run.",
